# 🧩 Why Sliding Window Works

Think of it like:

```
Expand → until valid
Shrink → until invalid
Repeat
```

This guarantees:

* Every character visited once by right pointer
* Every character removed once by left pointer

That’s why time complexity is:

👉 **O(n)**

