# 🎤 Interview Explanation in 20 Seconds

> We expand the window until all required characters are matched.
> Once valid, we shrink from the left to remove unnecessary characters.
> We keep updating the minimum window during valid states.
> This guarantees O(n) time because both pointers move at most n times.



